</span></div>
<div style="text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 21pt; background: white"><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<b><span style="color: red">日本</span></b>多摩川编码器</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> <b><span style="color: red">2500</span></b></span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">0.5%</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.1pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.95pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt"> 从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节省</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">2.   </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 18pt"> </span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">3.   德米特伺服</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机采用稀土永磁材料</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">SH-T</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，国内知名产家，每块磁通量相差不超过</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，（稳定性强），在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">个<br />
  小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">  耐温高</span></strong><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">：烧结钴基稀土永磁体的居里温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">850</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度，因此可适应高温环境工作，钴基稀土永磁体的工作温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">300</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">  温</span></b><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">度稳定性较好</span></strong>：钴基稀土永磁体的剩磁感应强度可逆温度系数可做到0.03%，其水平接近铝镍钴永磁体。</div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt; background: white"> </div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">4.   </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电源线及编码器线采用湖州长城漆包线，型号</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">180t</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">。</span></div>
<div><span style="font-size: 14pt">5</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．根据试验机要求</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">750W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">分两种转速，</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2000r 3000r </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，某些伺服品牌只有</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">扭距太单一，法兰分两种一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">80 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">（</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90<br />
      </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">同东元尺寸完全一样，不需要另加工其他零件，可以直接替换）<br />
</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">6.   </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">试验机定制</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1500W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">替换某些品牌</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1000W1000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机，扭距优于其他品牌，尺寸完全一样。价格差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">700</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">左右。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">7</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．伺服驱动器内置模块采用<b><span style="color: red">进口三菱</span></b></span><span style="font-size: 14pt">20A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> 30A 40A 50A </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">模块。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">8</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．德米特可以根据客户要求进行<b><span style="color: red">贴牌</span></b>处理，方便客户以自产品牌进行推广销售。<br />

<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<strong><span data-mce-style="color: red;" style="color: red">日本</span></strong>多摩川编码器</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt"><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red;" style="color: red">2500</span></strong></span><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red; font-size: 14pt;" style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></strong><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span></span></p>

<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    省</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">2. </span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><strong><span data-mce-style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt;" style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></strong><strong><span data-mce-style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt;" style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></strong></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>

<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    在</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">个小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></span></p>

<div class="tinymce-module fd-clr" data-mce-style="text-align: left;" style="text-align: left">
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<strong><span data-mce-style="color: red;" style="color: red">日本</span></strong>多摩川编码器</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt"><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red;" style="color: red">2500</span></strong></span><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red; font-size: 14pt;" style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></strong><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    0.5%</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    省</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">2. </span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><strong><span data-mce-style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt;" style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></strong><strong><span data-mce-style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt;" style="background-color: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></strong></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">3. 德米特伺服</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">电机采用稀土永磁材料</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">SH-T</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">，国内知名产家，每块磁通量相差不超过</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">，（稳定性强），</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">    在</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">个小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></span></p>
<p data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red; font-size: 16pt;" style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">   耐温高</span></strong><span data-mce-style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt;" style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">：<span data-mce-style="font-size: 12pt;" style="font-size: 12pt">烧结钴基稀土永磁体的居里温度可达</span></span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 12pt;" style="font-size: 12pt"><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">850</span><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">摄氏度</span><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">，因此可适应高温环境工作，钴基稀土永磁体的</span></span></span></p>
<p data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 12pt;" style="font-size: 12pt"><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">   工作温度可达</span><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">300</span><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">摄氏度</span><span data-mce-style="color: #111111;" style="color: #111111">。</span></span></span></p>
<p data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red; font-size: 16pt;" style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">   温</span></strong><strong><span data-mce-style="color: red; font-size: 16pt;" style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">度稳定性较好</span></strong>：<span data-mce-style="font-size: 12pt;" style="font-size: 12pt">钴基稀土永磁体的剩磁感应强度可逆温度系数可做到0.03%，其水平接近铝镍钴永</span></span></p>
<p data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 12pt;" style="font-size: 12pt">    磁体。</span></span></p>
<p data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆; color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt;" style="font-family: 幼圆; color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt"> </span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">4．</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">电源线及编码器线采用湖州长城漆包线，型号</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">180t</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">。</span></span></p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>
<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"><span data-mce-style="font-family: 幼圆;" style="font-family: 幼圆"><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">5．</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">根据某些行业要求</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">750W</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">分两种转速，</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">2000r 3000r</span><span data-mce-style="font-size: 14pt;" style="font-size: 14pt">，其他一些国产伺服电机只有</span></span></p>

<p align="left" data-mce-style="background-color: white;" style="background-color: white"> </p>

                <div id="ContentPlaceHolder1_divProductContent"><img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/150系列标准规格表(2).png" width="880" height="540" alt="" /><br />
<img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/60系列焊线定义(23).png" width="440" height="446" alt="" /><img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/DM470230P2-150(2).jpg" width="440" height="330" alt="" /><br />

<div style="text-align: center; text-indent: 22.1pt; margin: 17pt 0pt 16.5pt" align="center"><b><font size="6"><br />
德米特伺服电机定制特点</font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 21pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<b><span style="color: red">日本</span></b>多摩川编码器</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> <b><span style="color: red">2500</span></b></span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">0.5%</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.1pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.95pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节省</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">2. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 18pt"> </span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">3. 德米特伺服</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机采用稀土永磁材料</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">SH-T</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，国内知名产家，每块磁通量相差不超过</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，（稳定性强），在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">个小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">耐温高</span></strong><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">：烧结钴基稀土永磁体的居里温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">850</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度，因此可适应高温环境工作，钴基稀土永磁体的工作温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">300</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">温</span></b><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">度稳定性较好</span></strong>：钴基稀土永磁体的剩磁感应强度可逆温度系数可做到0.03%，其水平接近铝镍钴永磁体。</div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt; background: white"> </div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">4. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电源线及编码器线采用湖州长城漆包线，型号</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">180t</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">5</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．根据用户要求</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">750W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">分两种转速，</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2000r 3000r </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，某些伺服电机只有</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">扭距太单一，法兰分两种一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">80 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">（</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">同东元尺寸完全一样，不需要另加工其他零件，可以直接替换）。价格比其他伺服电机相差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">350</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -17.9pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.9pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">6. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">试验机行业定制</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1500W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">替换某品牌</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1000W1000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机，扭距大。价格差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">700</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">左右。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">7</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．伺服驱动器内置模块采用<b><span style="color: red">进口三菱</span></b></span><span style="font-size: 14pt">20A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> 30A 40A 50A </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">模块。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">8</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．德米特可以根据客户要求进行<b><span style="color: red">贴牌</span></b>处理，方便客户以自产品牌进行推广销售。<br />

                <div id="ContentPlaceHolder1_divProductContent"><div style="text-align: left; text-indent: 22.1pt; margin: 17pt 0pt 16.5pt;"><b><font size="6"><img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/150系列标准规格表(3).png" width="880" height="540" alt="" /><br />
<img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/60系列焊线定义(24).png" width="440" height="446" alt="" /><img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/DM470230P2-150(3).jpg" width="440" height="330" alt="" /><br />
<img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/150系列(5).png" width="880" height="392" alt="" /><br />
<br />
</font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: center; text-indent: 22.1pt; margin: 17pt 0pt 16.5pt;"><b><font size="6">德米特伺服电机定制特点</font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 21pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<b><span style="color: red">日本</span></b>多摩川编码器</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> <b><span style="color: red">2500</span></b></span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">0.5%</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.1pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.95pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节省</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">2. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 18pt"> </span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">3. 德米特伺服</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机采用稀土永磁材料</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">SH-T</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，国内知名产家，每块磁通量相差不超过</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，（稳定性强），在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">个小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">耐温高</span></strong><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">：烧结钴基稀土永磁体的居里温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">850</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度，因此可适应高温环境工作，钴基稀土永磁体的工作温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">300</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">温</span></b><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">度稳定性较好</span></strong>：钴基稀土永磁体的剩磁感应强度可逆温度系数可做到0.03%，其水平接近铝镍钴永磁体。</div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt; background: white"> </div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">4. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电源线及编码器线采用湖州长城漆包线，型号</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">180t</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">5</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．根据用户要求</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">750W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">分两种转速，</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2000r 3000r </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，某些伺服电机只有</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">扭距太单一，法兰分两种一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">80 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">（</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">同东元尺寸完全一样，不需要另加工其他零件，可以直接替换）。价格比其他伺服电机相差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">350</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -17.9pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.9pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">6. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">试验机行业定制</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1500W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">替换某品牌</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1000W1000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机，扭距大。价格差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">700</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">左右。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">7</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．伺服驱动器内置模块采用<b><span style="color: red">进口三菱</span></b></span><span style="font-size: 14pt">20A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> 30A 40A 50A </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">模块。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">8</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．德米特可以根据客户要求进行<b><span style="color: red">贴牌</span></b>处理，方便客户以自产品牌进行推广销售。<br />

<img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/60系列焊线定义(25).png" width="440" height="446" alt="" /><img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/DM470230P2-150(4).jpg" width="440" height="330" alt="" /><br />
<img src="/FCKeditorUploads/image/150系列(6).png" width="880" height="392" alt="" /><br />
<div style="text-align: center; text-indent: 22.1pt; margin: 17pt 0pt 16.5pt" align="center"><b><font size="6"><br />
德米特伺服电机定制特点</font></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -21pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 21pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">、德米特伺服电机内置编码器采用<b><span style="color: red">日本</span></b>多摩川编码器</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> <b><span style="color: red">2500</span></b></span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 14pt">线，</span></b><span style="font-size: 14pt">不需再外加编码器，位移优于士</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">0.5%</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.1pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 17.95pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">从成本上来讲：外置编码器成本能省掉</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右，加上相关零件也有至少</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元。共能节省</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">200</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt"><br />
2. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">采用防水航插（重强）</span><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 18pt"> </span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">防水性能均达到</span></b><b><span style="background: white; color: red; font-size: 18pt">IP67</span></b></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt"><br />
3. 德米特</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机采用稀土永磁材料</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">SH-T</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，国内知名产家，每块磁通量相差不超过</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，（稳定性强），在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">150</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">度高温淬火</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">个小时，反复三次，然后测试永磁材料不少于</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3%</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">！</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">耐温高</span></strong><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">：烧结钴基稀土永磁体的居里温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">850</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度，因此可适应高温环境工作，钴基稀土永磁体的工作温度可达</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">300</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">摄氏度</span><span style="color: #111111; font-size: 9.5pt">。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 15.75pt; background: white"><b><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">温</span></b><strong><span style="color: red; font-size: 16pt">度稳定性较好</span></strong>：钴基稀土永磁体的剩磁感应强度可逆温度系数可做到0.03%，其水平接近铝镍钴永磁体。</div>
<div style="line-height: 16.3pt; margin: 0pt; background: white"> </div>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">4. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电源线及编码器线采用湖州长城漆包线，型号</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">180t</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">。</span></div>
<div style="text-align: left; text-indent: -14pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt 14pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt"><br />
</span></div>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt">5</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．根据用户要求</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">750W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">分两种转速，</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">2000r 3000r </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">，某些伺服电机只有</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">3000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">扭距太单一，法兰分两种一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">80 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">一种</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90 </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">（</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">90</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">同东元尺寸完全一样，不需要另加工其他零件，可以直接替换）。价格比其他伺服电机相差在</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">350</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">元左右。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt"><br />
6. </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">试验机行业定制</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1500W </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">替换某品牌</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">1000W1000r</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">电机，扭距大。<br />
</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"><br />
7</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．伺服驱动器内置模块采用<b><span style="color: red">进口三菱</span></b></span><span style="font-size: 14pt">20A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt"> 30A 40A 50A </span><span style="font-size: 14pt">模块。</span></p>
<div style="text-align: left; margin: 0pt 0pt 5.45pt; background: white" align="left"><span style="font-size: 14pt">8</span><span style="font-size: 14pt">．德米特可以根据客户要求进行<b><span style="color: red">贴牌</span></b>处理，方便客户以自产品牌进行推广销售。<br />
<br />
